# Imagine that you are hired to enable data analytics; where would you start?

As a data engineer, I would be able to enable data analytics by starting with gathering appropriate requirements.

# How would you go about gathering requirements?

Identify the end-users such as the data scientist, data analyst, external clients and stakeholders.

Defining and understanding the scope of the requirement by;
-Highlighting how having a dataset can enable data analytics.
-Recognizing the source of the dataset that can enable data analytics.
-Collecting and Integrating datasets to enable data analytics.
-Transforming a dataset into a usable format for the end users.
-Storing and managing datasets to enable analytics.

